Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:06.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's time for the Sibylla Aurea Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monthly! ADR Bulletin Special{\i0}\N{\i1}Pair Versus Pair Competition!!{\i0}\NIt's time for the Sibylla Aurea Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:10.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monthly! ADR Bulletin Special{\i0}\N{\i1}Pair Versus Pair Competition!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:11.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monthly! ADR Bulletin Special{\i0}\N{\i1}Pair Versus Pair Competition!!{\i0}\NWe're going...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:12.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to determine which pair is worthy\Nof being called "Golden Priestesses"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:16.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina\NRIKA MORINAGA\N...to determine which pair is worthy\Nof being called "Golden Priestesses"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:21.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you'll be\Ncompeting in teams of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:25.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,After the last round, the pair,\Nor team, with the most points...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:29.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will receive an extremely\Nvaluable prize! Do your best, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:36.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's have each member\Nintroduce herself and their pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:40.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Michi Niino, and I play Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:42.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I play Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:46.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I play Neviril.\NMy name is Rieko Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:50.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,The pair's name is Lilies of the Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:53.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Ami Koshimizu,\Nand I play Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I play Kaim. Michiko Hosokoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I play Kaim. Michiko Hosokoshi.\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:00:58.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:00.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our pair's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the Mangoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:06.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Mamiko Noto, and I play Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:08.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mikako Takahashi. I play Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:11.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our pair's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Monotone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:14.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:15.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.08,0:01:17.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:20.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Michiru Aizawa, and I play Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:24.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um... Alty, right?\NI'm Megumi Toyoguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:26.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our pair's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:28.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Team Green!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:32.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Copycats! Copycats!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:33.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rip-off! Rip-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:37.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Copycats? Yes, but please\Nroot for us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:42.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, so here they are...\Nthe contestants of this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's the best couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun Compatibility Test!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:03.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,So let's start with\Na simple word association game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll give you\Na keyword related to Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:10.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you each write down\Nwhatever comes to mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:13.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,...using those writing boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:17.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Points will be awarded if both\Nteam members give the same answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:23.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll give you the first\Nkeyword now, and it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:27.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,In your opinion, what's the first\Nstep in becoming an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:30.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, everybody!\NGet your answers ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun related?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've been abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,From the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Becoming an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,It depends if we keep\Nthe story in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Becoming an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:54.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,How are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ding-ding-ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, now that time's up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:04.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's hear how Ms. Niino and\NMs. Takahashi, the Lilies, answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:13.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pretty long! When you start your first\Njob, start making your own money...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:21.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's so realistic. A part-time job...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:23.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,She even wrote it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:26.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then let's see your answer, Rieko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:29.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love{\i0}\NTa-da... Totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's like you're really holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:35.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's like you're really holding back.\NBut still, they're both mature answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:40.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,The answers are\Ntotally different, so no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:46.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, next up... Ami-chan\Nand Michiko-san, the Mangoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:50.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don't you show us at\Nthe same time? Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:55.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shopping alone (running first errand){\i0}\N{\i1}Going shopping by yourself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Running your first errand too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:03:59.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're definitely a good match, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:13.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next up, Mamiko-san and\NMeguko-chan, the Monotones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:20.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}20 years old Alcohol{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:26.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's "you can turn\N20 after you drink alcohol"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:31.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can drink alcohol\Nafter you turn 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, um, nothing doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:43.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,No good, no good.\NWrong answer, wrong answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:46.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.\NIt's Michiru-chan and Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:49.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go, green team. Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:53.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First Kiss (Smack!) Alcohol{\i0}\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should pair up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should pair up.\NYou can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:59.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I knew we'd agree on something...\NAnd it had to be this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess it's\Nthe generation gap or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:05.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yup, to be brutally honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:08.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all, you can't...\NYou can't yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I can't drink yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:15.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then on to the next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Question number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:21.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,What makes a woman beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:25.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,What makes a woman beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:31.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you please.\NWrite it down, write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:33.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay! We're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:41.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, which page\Ndid I write my answer on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,You wrote a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready? All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the Lilies again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:51.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Show us your answers.\NReady, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:56.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never bending her will to the very end!{\i0}\N{\i1}Her purity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,No good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, next. The Mangoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,To always be smiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:11.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, they're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:17.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Smiles equal kindness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't think they're equal at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:23.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,No good, no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:29.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next, the Monotones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:32.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:33.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:34.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Content.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:38.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, mine means "outside"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:43.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,So as long as it looks good\Non the outside, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:49.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we should write\Nthe opposite thing from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's another "no-good" answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, Team Green next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neviril-sama Being in love{\i0}\NWhat kind of answer is that? You\Nokay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:09.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I tried every which way\Nto come up with a teen's answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,An answer that evokes youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's up with that answer?\NNeviril-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because she's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:19.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,"All you have to be is beautiful."\N("Utsukushikereba soredeii.")
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,The theme song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, it is a typical Floe answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:28.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I guess for this corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:31.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,...l'll give the Mangoes\N10,000 points or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,10,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,So anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:42.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's it for\Nthe Simoun Compatibility Test!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:54.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Super-Difficult Simoun Cult Quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:59.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, so the rules are very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a quiz all about\Nwhat happens in the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll read show-related questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:10.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and I'd like you to write your\Nanswers on the writing boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:15.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,So let's get started. Question one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before their first flight in episode\None...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:22.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,...how many times did\NNeviril and Amuria kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that is super difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before their first flight in episode\None...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:33.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,...how many times did\NNeviril and Amuria kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before their flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:48.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Five, four, three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chu-chu, chu-chu-chu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,What kind of a sound effect was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:59.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd make it more quizlike.\NEach team, show your answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,First up, the Lilies. Ready, set, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:04.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Three times.\NWhich teams answered "three times"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, can we get extra points for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,That side interests me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:27.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, this isn't\Na manga-drawing class, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:30.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, Monotones, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ta-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,1.5 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:34.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where does the 0.5 come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:37.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where does the 0.5 come from?\NWrong, wrong, wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:40.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they stopped at the last second...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,We averaged it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:49.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, the correct answer is twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:56.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we're closest! We're closest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're closer than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,You all said it was three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:11.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since you two were so cute getting\Nall worked up, I'll give you points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:21.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Enough! They told me I could\Nbe biased and partial, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:23.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:27.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,In episode two, when Neviril\Nwas wearing civilian clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what color was her bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Neviril question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Answer, answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:36.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Think, think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, her hair's pink, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:54.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Five, four, three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kon-kon-kon-kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?\NIt was just a whisper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start\Nwith Team Lilies' answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:08.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,How elegant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:12.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look at that smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look at that smile!\NShe's brimming with confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:18.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,If she gets this one wrong,\Nit's going to be funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril's answer is purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:29.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, the Mangoes next. Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:33.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go! An orangish-brownish color.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:36.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,An orangish-brownish color?\NWhich is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, it's kind of subtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,More of which?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mottled!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean marbled?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:45.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,In keeping with the Simoun theme...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,In keeping with the Simoun theme...\NPlease accept our answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then next...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:50.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,H-How cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:54.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,To the next answer. Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,A pink flower pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Her hair's pink, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:04.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since her hair's pink,\Nshe decides to color coordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:08.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,When she has to ponder\Nbecoming a man or woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:11.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Since I've got pink hair,\Nlet's go with a flower pattern!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,"It won't do without it."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's very typical.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:22.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,On to the next team,\NTeam Green. Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go. Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:24.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:29.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I seem to remember it was\Na darkish color, like purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:30.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:33.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like brown.\NNo, not brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:36.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,The correct answer is brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:43.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on! Hey, MC!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Orangish-brownish" isn't brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:48.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Orangish-brownish" isn't brown!\NI think it could look orange too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:59.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!\NYay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:02.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim! Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:08.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I'm counting that\Nas a correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's it for\Nthe Super-Difficult Cult Quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:22.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun Anything and\NEverything Case Files.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:28.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, in this corner,\NI'll ask you to answer questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:33.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,...about inside stories,\Nthings that happened during ADR.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it's a kiss-and-tell contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:38.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll pick a question out of this box...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:40.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Written by you before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:45.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I'll start drawing, and I'd like\Nto discuss these stories with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm agreeing with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:52.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,The keyword... Okay, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:58.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Surprised to be in a place where\Nwomen gave their all playing men!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:13:59.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Meguko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:08.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right from episode one, everyone\Ndid a valiant job playing old men...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:11.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...throwing themselves into it,\Nand I was very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:17.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,When they did the first session,\Nyou could hear laughter in the booth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,The staff was cracking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:26.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because usually, having a girl's voice\Ncoming out of an old guy's mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:30.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,It never happened in anime till now.\NIt shouldn't ever happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:35.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Government Official{\i0}\N{\i1}Voiced by Megumi Toyoguchi{\i0}\NYour daughter is\Nan outstanding pilot, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:38.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we signed up for old guys,\Nwe'd say, "This one!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:40.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like the somewhat chubby one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:46.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd credit us\Nfor the old guys we played.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're not old guys! Like "soldier"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:00.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Basically, I have very few lines.\NAnd no ad libs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:02.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:07.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,You see, in the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:13.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,The thing is... basically,\NRimone doesn't have a lot of dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had quite a few ad libbed lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:21.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,But one by one, they'd say,\N"Not needed, not needed, not needed."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:25.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,So she hardly had dialogue.\NOnly a line or two when she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:30.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I thought, "I wish I could\Ntalk as much as everyone else."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was my secret dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not that it was accidental...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,They pretty much delete everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:41.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,So in the nondialogue\Nparts of the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like when they write "turns around"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'd normally write "ad lib"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:51.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,But as far as this show, they're like,\N"We don't need this. Cross that out."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:55.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,But when you think you don't\Nhave any lines, they add something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:58.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like to turn around violently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like, "Hah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:02.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hard to know\Nwhere to draw the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:06.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,And sometimes they throw\Nland mines like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:10.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Set traps for you in your path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:25.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea Battle\NPair Versus Pair Competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here are the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:36.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, which team will\Nclaim the "Golden Priestess" title?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:41.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've taken the liberty of deciding,\Nand it's a biased and partial decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:46.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, well, what did\Nyou think of the games?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun? Was it hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was really motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:53.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I drew some pictures too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I have a feeling we're gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you score?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:04.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,The green in your clothes\Nis even more dazzling now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,You didn't get any points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let me\Nannounce the winning team!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:13.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,The winners are the Mangoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:18.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Winners{\i0}\N{\i1}The Mangoes{\i0}\NYay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, you put up a good fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,As expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:24.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you performed well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:29.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now then, the Mangoes will be\Npresented with this Simoun candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please shower your\Nkisses on this candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:59.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, so the Mangoes\Nended up winning today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I'm glad we all got\Nto have a good time today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:05.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please keep watching Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please keep watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,So the Sibylla Aurea Battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:17.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Sibylla Aurea Battle\NPair Versus Pair Competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:20.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's all, folks! Everyone, bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:26.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
